  "description": "防幻觉skill - 行为层面的AI幻觉防护，不是告诉AI不要编，而是给它一套具体操作流程来避免编",
  "author": "CherryAI",
  "tags": ["hallucination", "accuracy", "verification", "fact-checking", "safety"],
